data.text: @bubblegenius Me too, it was just over-use abuse. They guy was running a not-so-secret "secret" dorm bar called Eileen's that everyone new about and he was just advertising. We finally got enough people together to let him know we'd "Narc" on him if he didn't stop!

@T4booboo I've always loved Dexy's but could do without hearing that particular song ever again.

https://t.co/W1ZnUxSdBC

@bubblegenius You mean of "Come on Eileen" fame? Oy, don't get me started about the idiot in my dorm that played that song ten times a night for months on end. Although there's nothing wrong with the song I still can't listen to it.

Worse, my R.A. was named Steve Miller and you can guess ...
